Body: Description: We are experiencing problems updating the back-end and front-end. This is a recurring issue; previously, support had to assist us in performing the same operation manually. We need help updating this time and resolving the issue so autonomous updates can be done independently in the future.
What We've Learned Updated: the customer tried to update to 5941 which most likely was not available due to the drip release phase.
Next Steps Updated: waiting for the update to be available in GA and then update
